                    <span>This book has a magical combination of real life stories interwoven with principles and facts based on research. Not an easy mix to achieve. Hats off to these authors!<BR>Evonne Weinhaus,<BR>Co-author of Stop Struggling With Your Teen<BR>& Stop Struggling With Your Child</span>
                  
              
